255
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:06,000
Why d'you always have him around... Surely not at this age? Just... Let the lad play...

256
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:09,946
Siddiq!

257
00:30:12,340 --> 00:30:16,561
Show the young lad around our lawn. Get him some juice, okay?

258
00:30:16,561 --> 00:30:18,178
Come.
-Go.

259
00:30:18,178 --> 00:30:22,865
And get some sherbet for us too.

260
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:28,448
I'm sure you wouldn't mind some...?

261
00:30:28,948 --> 00:30:32,980
