262
00:30:32,980 --> 00:30:34,001
Ten grand...

263
00:30:34,001 --> 00:30:35,467
Ten grand... Twenty...

264
00:30:35,467 --> 00:30:37,202
Ten grand... Twenty... Fifty...

265
00:30:37,202 --> 00:30:38,523
Ten grand... Twenty... Fifty... A hundred...

266
00:30:38,523 --> 00:30:39,636
Ten grand... Twenty... Fifty... A hundred... Two, or if you will...

267
00:30:39,636 --> 00:30:42,647
Ten grand... Twenty... Fifty... A hundred... Two, or if you will, five...

268
00:30:43,080 --> 00:30:48,281
It depends entirely on how much you can...

269
00:30:51,080 --> 00:30:52,947
That'll be enough, Mr Malik!

270
00:30:52,947 --> 00:30:55,178
I'll take my leave.

271
00:30:55,320 --> 00:30:56,530
Where are you off to?

272
00:30:56,530 --> 00:30:59,230
Get off me, Mr Malik!

273
00:30:59,854 --> 00:31:06,755
You're -- You're getting it all wrong! Get off me! Geroff --

274
00:31:26,790 --> 00:31:30,753
One more step and I'll jump!

275
00:31:31,570 --> 00:31:34,760
I ain't seeing this act for the first time.

276
00:31:34,760 --> 00:31:40,443
The last time someone said that, I said, 'Be my guest'.

277
00:31:40,443 --> 00:31:43,150
Scared the pants off her...

278
00:31:43,150 --> 00:31:46,398
What a shame...

279
00:31:46,398 --> 00:31:48,947
I swear I'll kill myself!

280
00:31:48,947 --> 00:31:55,732
Big words... Ain't gonna believe it until I see it... Go on...

281
00:32:37,780 --> 00:32:39,283
Nadia...

282
00:32:39,543 --> 00:32:40,954
Nadia...

283
00:32:41,310 --> 00:32:42,813
Nadia...

284
00:32:42,992 --> 00:32:45,653
Wasn't it fair? What I did?

285
00:32:45,653 --> 00:32:47,270
Nadia?

286
00:32:47,270 --> 00:32:50,160
Did I do something wrong?

287
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:51,852
Nadia?

288
00:32:52,110 --> 00:32:55,190
I just avenged you...

289
00:33:12,500 --> 00:33:14,103
Roshni...

290
00:33:17,390 --> 00:33:19,843
R -- Roshni...

291
00:33:23,380 --> 00:33:25,060
Roshni!

292
00:33:26,580 --> 00:33:28,398
Roshni...?

293
00:33:41,250 --> 00:33:43,204
Roshni...

294
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:53,460
Roshni...!

295
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:58,922
My girl... Where are you?

296
00:34:22,983 --> 00:34:24,218
Sir?

297
00:34:24,218 --> 00:34:26,844
I'd like a cuppa.
-'Sec!

298
00:34:36,080 --> 00:34:37,098
Hello?

299
00:34:37,098 --> 00:34:44,640
Our knight's willing to put everything on the line for his princess, but this time around, she's not even his! Never was, never will be!

300
00:34:44,640 --> 00:34:46,130
Why'd you call me?

301
00:34:46,130 --> 00:34:57,528
Thought I'd congratulate you. The man who'd jump in to save so much as a dead leaf falling from the tree etched with his love's name...

302
00:34:57,528 --> 00:35:11,230
Pure love, blind love, selfless love... There's a thousand ways to love, but yours is the thousand-and-fifty-first - pig-headed love!

303
00:35:11,230 --> 00:35:16,740
You could sacrifice your life for her, but the most she'd ever say is 'Thank you'.

304
00:35:16,740 --> 00:35:21,030
There are no ways to love...

305
00:35:21,030 --> 00:35:27,215
It's the way of those willing to live and die for the oath.

306
00:35:30,650 --> 00:35:33,466
But you won't get it.

307
00:35:33,466 --> 00:35:36,332
What would you know love?

308
00:35:36,531 --> 00:35:46,420
You only know hatred... It's what defines you, it's the only thing you ever feel... And perhaps the only thing you believe in.

309
00:35:46,420 --> 00:35:49,663
Ain't so easy for you to get it...

310
00:35:54,740 --> 00:36:04,830
I feel like cracking up... Doubling up in stitches until I'm all in tears... But my eyes fall on the kid... <i>Her</i> kid...

311
00:36:04,830 --> 00:36:12,283
I so wish a laugh could knock your slumbering morality up.

312
00:36:13,545 --> 00:36:15,436
No, Adam...

313
00:36:15,810 --> 00:36:18,290
Don't say that...

314
00:36:18,290 --> 00:36:21,338
I'd mind it if anyone else said that...

315
00:36:21,338 --> 00:36:25,099
But... Hearing it from you... Pains me...

316
00:36:34,240 --> 00:36:37,960
What if I don't want to be loved back?

317
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:43,640
It's sinful to ask for anything in return when you find happiness in theirs...

318
00:36:43,640 --> 00:36:48,318
It'd be so insulting to our hearts...

319
00:36:51,990 --> 00:36:57,600
First time in years someone's bitter words have pained me...

320
00:36:57,600 --> 00:37:01,000
Like it's someone who actually cares...

